Authorship and derivation
--------------------------

Fieldnotes is a fork of ProofPoll (https://github.com/WeAreFlowsta/ProofPoll),
a verified-polling application created by Flowsta. ProofPoll is the foundation
on which Fieldnotes is built — the Holochain conductor lifecycle, Flowsta Vault
identity integration, DNA migration system, and encrypted-data patterns are
ProofPoll's work, adapted here. We are grateful for it.

ProofPoll is licensed under the MIT License. That original licence is preserved
verbatim in LICENSE.MIT and continues to apply to the portions of this work
derived from ProofPoll. The MIT License permits this relicensing, provided the
original copyright notice and licence text are retained — which they are.

