What changed
------------

Fieldnotes repurposes ProofPoll's polling substrate into a structured
scenario-testing tool: polls and votes became Items, Responses, and Findings;
a validate-enforced administrator gate, an archive primitive, a bulk scenario
importer, and an advisory private-data check were added. The shared Holochain
and Flowsta foundation, and the principled divergence in how each application
treats public versus private data, are the subject of a hAppenings community
article on convergent evolution in the Holochain ecosystem.
